// Inertia — components visibly resisting evolution
component Legacy CNI Assets [0.55, 0.45] inertia
Critical National Infrastructure (CNI)->Legacy CNI Assets
// Inertia form: sunk capital + re-architecture cost (CNI rewire is multi-decade)

component Domestic Fab Base [0.22, 0.30] inertia
Semiconductors->Domestic Fab Base
// Inertia form: political capital + second-sourcing risk (fabs are geopolitical)

// Evolution movements (scenario — NOT a forecast; cf. climatic pattern)
evolve Digital Sovereignty 0.45
evolve Cyber Theatre 0.55
evolve Digital-Chain Awareness 0.40
evolve Cyber Capability 0.55
evolve Semiconductors 0.45

// Notes — where sovereignty is industrialised vs. contested
note Industrialised infrastructure [0.15, 0.88]
note Contested + fragile frontier [0.75, 0.22]
note Legitimacy feedback loop [0.80, 0.32]
